com.vectorprint.report.data.types

Class Formatter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vectorprint.report.data.types.Formatter

  • public class Formatter
extends Object
    formats ReportValue's according to format Strings. Uses Locale.getDefault(), which can be changed specifying system properties (i.e. -Duser.language=nl -Duser.country=NL).
    Author:
    Eduard Drenth at VectorPrint.nl
